channel.title: Compiling Error - Fix
channel.description:
Alright so everyones saying help me with compiler what you need to do is go to Computer/Local C drive/Program files(x86)/Java Copy all files in java and go to Computer/Local C Drive/Program Files/Java and paste everything there.
When your done try compiling and it has to work 90%. If it doesnt work you probaly need a better compiler i will make a better guide soon.
